<i>noun</i>: 겸허 [겸허], 겸양 [겨먕] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>겸허 [겸허]</dt><br>
<dd>modesty; humbleness; humility</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체 하지 않고 스스로 자신을 낮춤.</dd><br>
<dd>Not showing off and voluntarily acting humbly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>겸양 [겨먕]</dt><br>
<dd>humbleness; modesty; humility; diffidence</dd><br>
<dd>자기를 낮추면서 남에게 양보함.</dd><br>
<dd>Acts humbly and gives way to others.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>